INSERT IGNORE INTO `quest_request_items` (`ID`, `EmoteOnComplete`, `EmoteOnIncomplete`, `CompletionText`, `VerifiedBuild`) VALUES (67027, 0, 0, 'Hi all Small Guide how to farm Reputation for Wrathion and Sabellian . See My Video with all location of NPC, Rares, shops ect. - https://youtu.be/RclLJYzxn-8 See My Video for 2x4 farm party if need it - https://youtu.be/peR4489d-o4 How to do 2x4 party in spoiler: First go on spot wher you want to do 2x4 farm. Spots: 24.6 58.1 In Basement 28.3 58.8 25 56 in Basement Then Create party in LRG call &quot;2x4 Key Basement WMoff gr1&quot; When You get to 5 please give someone who know that He need to keep max 4 please in party. Then open new party call it &quot;2x4 Key Basement WMoff gr2&quot; No just keep 4 people in 2 party Mobs will start spawn much faster and farm will go faster to. . Step 1: Do Quest Allegiance to One pick side Wrathion or Sabellian ( but leter you can farm reputation for bouth sides ) then You will get Weekly Quest Keys of Loyalty . Go quick LFG for Quest and collect from mobs 30 Key Fragments and 3 Key Framing to make Restored Obsidian Key . Now You can finish your weekly quest ( You will get 1000 rep for Wrathion or Sabellian and 100 Valdrakken Accord . Step 2: Start farming Restored Obsidian Key by finding/making party. Do events for delivered Keys. You can give Keys to 4 NPC but only 2 of them will give you reputation. All NPV next to them have other NPC showing over head how many Keys left to start event. 4 NPC Descryption, events and shop: 1. Wrathion - Need 20 Restored Obsidian Key to start Event Clearing the Vault now you can kill Rare Shas\'ith is in cave enter 27.2 60.9 just follow Miraveth . For making better reputation You can buy items from Atticus Belle 26.5 62.5 2. Sabellian 27.6 56.5 - Need 20 Restored Obsidian Key to start Event Death\'s Shadow now you can kill Rare Death\'s Shadow is spawn around 30 54 but He is flying around You need to pull him. For making better reputation You can buy 