 NPC You Will get Obsidian Cache but ( i think ) every 10th Obsidian Strongbox open only if you have lvl 70 but you can collect them how many you want if you lower lvl. Do Quests as well they will give you reputation to. All rare in this location are part of Adventurer of The Waking Shores . How to get Mount Loyal Magmammoth : Small Guide How to get Loyal Magmammoth , Grand Theft Mammoth and how to do Petty Theft Mammoth . To get this Mount You need to do in order: See My Video for Loyal Magmammoth - https://youtu.be/fcqUZLXEfUw See My Video for Petty Theft Mammoth with map - https://youtu.be/8lhgrzd3VrI 1. Loyal Magmammoth To get this Mount You need to do in order: Step 1. ======================== Reach max reputation with Sabellian and Wrathion True Friend. When You get it You will reach Achievements The Obsidian Bloodline and Loyalty to the Prince . Step 2. ======================== When You reach max reputation You will be able to Buy 3 item. First Buy 2 Items: - Sturdy Obsidian Glasses - Buy from Lorena Belle or Atticus Belle . /way #2022 26.54 62.46 Atticus Belle - Netherforged Lavaproof Boots - Buy from Samia Inkling or Xaldrass . /way #2022 27.71 56.32 Xaldrass When Get this 2 items Go to buy Magmammoth Harness from Yries Lightfingers is on TOP in Obsidian Citadel /way #2022 26.39 55.42 Yries Lightfingers Step 3. ======================= Now go to mount Tame Magmammoth /way 33.37 72.06, But at first kill mob next to it Qalashi Necksnapper . If You still have problem with mount Tame Magmammoth You need to dismount and do /reload. When You mount Tame Magmammoth use Magmammoth Harness . Loyal Magmammoth will be added automatically as well You will reach Achievement Grand Theft Mammoth . 2. Petty Theft Mammoth is a simple Achievement, You need to mount 4 Tame Magmammoth and move on them to Mammoth-Tamer Tavok . You can have same problem with jumping on Tame Magmammoth but is same solution, You need to dismount then /reload then You will see arrow to jump on Tame Magmammoth . Locations: /way #2022 39.65 54.91 Mammoth-Tamer Tavok /way #2022 66.34 24.46 Scalecracker Keep /way #2022 37.10 44.53 Smoldering Perch /way #2022 33.42 72.09 Burning Ascent /way #2022 23.60 71.38 Dragonbane Keep Care when You mount Tame Magmammoth he have his HP when mobs will attack You Mount will lose HP. Care as well on lava mount will not loss HP but You will lose a lot don\'t die XD. Hope that all xD Hope That Help You :)', 0);
